Predicted values

Source: R/get_predicted.R
get_predicted.Rd

Returns values predicted by a model (i.e., fitted values).

get_predicted(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A model.
...

Passed down to residuals(), if possible.

Examples

x <- lm(Sepal.Length ~ Petal.Width * Species, data=iris)
get_predicted(x)
